Oh. my God. it's okay.

507
00:32:27.072 --> 00:32:28.782
They're here. They're here.

508
00:32:28.823 --> 00:32:31.159
We're gonna get you
out of this. okay? [sighs]

509
00:32:39.542 --> 00:32:45.965
