time doesn't make it go away.
but it-- it helps.

530
00:33:47.277 --> 00:33:48.945
-What do you mean?

531
00:33:50.447 --> 00:33:53.742
-My-- my dad was my best friend
when I was little.

532
00:33:56.619 --> 00:33:58.204
You know.
he-- he was around a lot.

533
