563
00:35:25.542 --> 00:35:26.876
I was never pregnant. I--

564
00:35:28.545 --> 00:35:30.296
I can't get pregnant.

565
00:35:30.338 --> 00:35:32.257
I had a botched abortion
when I was fifteen.

566
