I lied a lot.

576
00:36:00.201 --> 00:36:01.536
And I don't wanna lie anymore.

577
00:36:03.621 --> 00:36:06.791
I don't know why I'm telling you
this right now. I'm sorry. I'm--

578
00:36:06.833 --> 00:36:09.002
I'm-- This doesn't
even matter anymore.

579
00:36:09.044 --> 00:36:10.253
