you know.

607
00:38:09.330 --> 00:38:11.833
We just let ya live.
so we could use ya.

608
00:38:11.875 --> 00:38:14.044
-Mm.
-We've got leverage on ya.

609
00:38:14.085 --> 00:38:15.462
-Leverage?

610
