615
00:38:34.272 --> 00:38:36.399
Shampoo bottles from the dacha.
We've got alla that.

616
00:38:36.441 --> 00:38:37.901
-Don't we?
-Mm-hmm.

617
00:38:37.942 --> 00:38:39.944
-Yeah.

618
00:38:39.986 --> 00:38:42.322
You murdered those women.
