to manipulate?

622
00:38:49.329 --> 00:38:50.455
-I don't think
that'd be very good.

623
00:38:50.497 --> 00:38:51.664
-No. that would be very bad.

624
00:38:51.706 --> 00:38:53.583
-Yeah. what do you want?

625
00:38:53.625 --> 00:38:54.793
How are you gonna use
your leverage?

626
00:38:54.834 --> 00:38:56.086
