call a people person.

650
00:39:57.647 --> 00:40:00.734
It's hard to tell you apart.
two young Americans.

651
00:40:00.775 --> 00:40:02.777
Long hair. big eyebrows.

652
00:40:02.819 --> 00:40:06.239
But yes. yes. yes.

653
00:40:06.281 --> 00:40:08.283
