-Bea. do you smell smoke?

708
00:45:51.793 --> 00:45:53.420
You smell that?

709
00:45:55.505 --> 00:45:59.092
Fuck. Fuck. uh. Bea.
There's a lot of smoke.

710
00:46:00.343 --> 00:46:01.970
We have to go. right now.

711
00:46:02.012 --> 00:46:04.264
