755
00:48:33.663 --> 00:48:36.124
♪ You will never
quench the fire ♪

756
00:48:36.166 --> 00:48:38.668
♪ You'll give in
to your desire ♪

757
00:48:38.835 --> 00:48:42.297
♪ When the stranger
comes along ♪

758
00:48:42.339 --> 00:48:48.970
[♪]
